dc_description_s: 1 map : color ; 34 x 68 cm, folded to 17 x 10 cm|English title should read: Plan of Yokohama.|Copperplate print.|In Japanese and English.|Oriented with north to the lower right.|Relief shown pictorially.|Includes 2 insets, lists of block and bridge names, and distance charts.|Shows views of tourist attractions.|05 Engraved by Shimura Senkyō.|05 Engraved by 志村千郷.
